window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The easy part was getting in. The hard part will be surviving until the end.</b></p> <p>Ray thought he was through the worst the game had to offer. I mean, lich kings, vampires, and the dark one himself? Boy was he wrong.</p> <p>Potential new enemies are about to storm the gates. Lands need exploring and evil cultists' heads need chopping.</p> <p>Because when the horn bellows for a hero, people like you and Ray answer. Hone that imagination, grab your dice, and get ready, this one is going to be a doozy. Start listening today!</p>"; 
